The paper deals with the problem of approximate nearest neighbor search, which is a fundamental problem in databases and data mining. The proposed algorithm involves graph-based methods, which are commonly used in computer science for data analysis and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
